{"lemma":"بَرْقَة","slug":"بَرْقَة","root":"برقة","root_slug":"برقة","root_link":"/words/roots/برقة","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2317","n2318"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2317","headword_ar":"بَرْقَةٌ","root":"brq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[app. an inf. n. of un., signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A flash of lightning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wbS","text_ar":"وبص"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A fit of confusion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perplexity, affecting one in such a manner that he is unable to see his right course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2318","headword_ar":"بُرْقَةٌ","root":"brq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quantity of lightning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xxiv. 43, TA:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroqN","text_ar":"بُرْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or [this is a coll. gen. n., of which the former is the n. un.; or, probably, it is a mistranscription, and] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraqN","text_ar":"بُرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", also pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buruqN","text_ar":"بُرُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd ubi suprà.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rugged ground in which are stones and sand and earth mixed together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the stones thereof mostly white, but some being red, and black, and the earth white and of a whitish dust-colour, and sometimes by its side are meadows"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoD","text_ar":"رَوْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"); (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboraqu","text_ar":"اَبْرَقُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqaA='u","text_ar":"بَرْقَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion of such land"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroD","text_ar":"اَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqaA='u","text_ar":"بَرْقَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which consists of tracts containing black stones mixed with white sand, and which, when spacious, is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboraqu","text_ar":"اَبْرَقُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK:) [and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mountain mixed with sand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboraqu","text_ar":"اَبْرَقُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroqapN","text_ar":"بُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraqN","text_ar":"بُرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biraAqN","text_ar":"بِرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (JK, S;) and that of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrq","text_ar":"ابرق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abaAriqu","text_ar":"اَبَارِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, K,) after the manner of a subst., because the quality of a subst. is predominant in it; (TA;) and that of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brqA='","text_ar":"برقا=ء","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqaAwaAtN","text_ar":"بَرْقَاوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (As, IAar, S, K.) The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraq","text_ar":"بُرَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":191},{"kind":"text","text":"country of the Arabs are more than a hundred; and are distinguished by particular adjuncts, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroqapN AlA^avomaAdi","text_ar":"بُرْقَةٌ الاَثْمَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroqapu AlA^ajaAwili","text_ar":"بُرْقَةُ الاَجَاوِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (K.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qunofu*u buroqapK","text_ar":"قُنْفُذُ بُرْقَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hedge-hog of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brqp","text_ar":"برقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"], like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~u kudoyapi","text_ar":"ضَبُّ كُدْيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) ―         -b2-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"colour denoted by the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboraqu","text_ar":"اَبْرَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": in a mountain,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mixture of blackness and whiteness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqobaA='u","text_ar":"حَقْبَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoqabu","text_ar":"اَحْقَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Paucity of grease"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gravy"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in food."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","JK","IAar"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}